Hey there,

I hope this ends up where it should, and if not, apologies!

ddccontrol 0.5.2 does not support my monitors. I think they are somewhat
common, so the output for "LANG= LC_ALL= ddccontrol -p -c -d" is attached.
It is still working though! Using `gddccontrol` I am able to change the
settings of the monitors.

The three Dell monitors are U2415 and 2x U2414H. I'm running Manjaro with
the 5.15.28-1 Kernel.

If there's anything I can do to help further, I'm willing to do so.

Best wishes,
Watte

